@page
@model Trendify.Pages.ContactEmailModel

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    
<style>
        .about-us {
            
            padding: 50px 0;
            background-color: #d8e8e4;
            border: 2px thick #333; /* Adjust border styles as needed */
            border-radius: 20px;

        }

            .about-us h1 {
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 36px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #333; /* Heading color */
            }

            .about-us h2 {
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-top: 20px;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                color: #555; /* Subheading color */
            }

            .about-us p {
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.5;
                margin-left:100px;
                margin-right: 100px;
                color: #777; /* Paragraph text color */
            }

            .about-us a {
                color: #007bff; /* Link color */
                text-decoration: none;
            }

                .about-us a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .member-image {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 0 auto 10px;
        }

            .member-image img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                object-fit: cover;
            }

      
        .border-image {
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #333; /* Adjust border styles as needed */
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: #fff; /* Text color on the border image */
        }


     


        /* Style the form container */
        .form-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: #d8e8e4;
        }

            /* Style form headings */
            .form-container h3 {
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                color: #333;
            }

            /* Style form labels */
            .form-container label {
                font-size: 18px;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #555;
            }

            /* Style form input fields */
            .form-container .form-group input[type="text"],
            .form-container .form-group textarea {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                border-radius: 5px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            /* Style form validation error messages */
            .form-container .text-danger {
                color: #ff0000;
            }


                /* Style the submit button on hover */
                .form-container button[type="submit"]:hover {
                background-color: #8f9696;
                }

        .space{
            padding:50px;
        }
</style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="space"></div>
    <section style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start;">
        <div class="container" style="flex: 1;">
            
            <div class="team-member">
                <div class="member-image">
                    <img src="~/images/yaman.jpg" alt="Yaman">
                </div>
                <h2 style="font-size:17px;">Yaman Ayoun</h2>
                <p>
                    Full stack Web Developer in ASP.Net
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="team-member">
                <div class="member-image">
                    <img src="~/images/abd.png" alt="Abdelrahman">
                </div>
                <h2 style="font-size:17px;">Abdelrahman shaheen</h2>
                <p>
                    Full stack Web Developer in ASP.Net
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="flex: 1;">
            
            <form method="post" class="form-container form-inline">
                <h3 style="text-align:center">Contact Us</h3>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label asp-for="Contacts.Subject">Subject:</label>
                    <input asp-for="Contacts.Subject" class="form-control" />
                    <span asp-validation-for="Contacts.Subject" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label asp-for="Contacts.Description">Description:</label>
                    <textarea asp-for="Contacts.Description" class="form-control"></textarea>
                    <span asp-validation-for="Contacts.Description" class="text-danger"></span>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="space"></div>
    <section class="about-us">
        
            <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>Welcome to Trendify, your one-stop destination for online shopping. Trendify is an e-commerce web application designed to provide a seamless shopping experience for customers. With a wide range of products and user-friendly features, Trendify makes shopping enjoyable and convenient.</p>

            <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2023, Your E-commerce Store has been serving customers around the world. We started as a small team with a passion for providing unique and affordable products to our customers. Over the years, we have grown into a leading e-commerce platform, constantly evolving to meet the changing needs of our customers.</p>

            <h2>Our Team</h2>
            <p>We are a dedicated team of professionals who are committed to making your shopping experience enjoyable. Our team includes experts in various fields, from product selection to customer support:
                To learn more about the developers’ experiences, you can read more...</p>

        <h2>Customer Satisfaction</h2>
        <p>Your satisfaction is our top priority. Our dedicated customer support team is available to assist you with any questions or concerns you may have. We strive to make your shopping experience enjoyable and hassle-free.</p>

            
        
    </section>
    <div class="space"></div>
   


    </body>

</html>
